latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sharing all my favourites from @viseartofficialindia and creating this super easy playful summer date makeup look. I love their contour, highlighter & blush palette and always make sure it is in my personal vanity even if I’m travelling, their individual highlighters are spot on for that extra oomph. Don’t miss on their super luxurious brushes.
